ayered Petal Frame<\/h2>\r\nIf you want something traditional for your home but are also looking for a little playfulness and experimentation, you can choose this wall mirror with its multi-layered petal frame. The petal frame has been designed to resemble a magnificent chrysanthemum flower made from metal sheets that are specifically cut, layered and finished in antique brass with a black finish to it. It creates a fascinating texture that makes a bold statement against a brick accent wall and a three-legged wooden side table.\r\n\r\nHope this blog has inspired you enough to experiment with the overall look of your home. Pick a few from among the best wall mirror designs that capture your personality and heart. Let your mirrors do the talking and become a good conversation starter for guests!\r\n\r\n<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-8171 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/21180948\/petal-frame-wall-mirror-design-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Wall mirror design with multi-layered petal frame creates a fascinating texture against a brick accent wall.\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/21180948\/petal-frame-wall-mirror-design-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/21180948\/petal-frame-wall-mirror-design-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/21180948\/petal-frame-wall-mirror-design-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/21180948\/petal-frame-wall-mirror-design-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/>\r\n\r\n<span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:513,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;12&quot;:0}\"><div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"i